l|en|Las Vegas Weekly|拉斯維加斯週刊|Las Vegas Weekly}}|publisher={{tsl|en|The Greenspun Corporation|The Greenspun Corporation|The Greenspun Corporation}}|date=2013-09-21|accessdate=2013-09-23}}</ref> 。10月5日，希拉現身「[[週六夜現場|週六夜現場]]」其中一集作為主持跟音樂嘉賓。她出現於節目多場短劇中，包括惡搞〈青春大暴走〉的「We Did Stop (The Government)」短劇，以影射[[2013年美国联邦政府关闭事件|2013年美国联邦政府关闭事件]]，她亦演唱了〈青春大暴走〉跟〈愛情破壞球〉的原音樂版<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2013/10/06/miley-cyrus-saturday-night-live/2930265/|title=Miley Cyrus steers clear of controversy on 'SNL'|last=Mansfield|first=Brian|newspaper=USA Today|date=2013-10-06|accessdate=2013-10-06}}</ref>。她於翌日在「[[今天_(NBC)|今天]]」上演唱了該兩首歌曲，作為豐田演唱會系列的一部分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.today.com/popculture/miley-cyrus-says-she-doesnt-ever-really-plan-offend-8C11339820|title=Miley Cyrus says she doesn't 'ever really plan to offend'|last=Dawn|first=Randee|work=[[今天_(NBC)|Today]]|publisher=NBCUniversal|date=2013-10-07|accessdate=2013-10-07}}</ref>。10月8日，她在[[時報廣場|時報廣場]]的{{tsl|en|Planet Hollywood|荷里活星球|荷里活星球}}舉行專輯簽名會<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/08/14/miley-cyrus-does-all-white-for-her-album-launch-and-yes-there-was-a-crop-top_n_7356814.html|title=Miley Cyrus Does All White For Her Album Launch (And Yes, There Was A Crop Top)|last=Sitch|first=Daisy|publisher=My Daily. AOL|date=2013-10-09|accessdate=2013-10-09}}</ref>，並現身「{{tsl|en|Late Night with Jimmy Fallon|吉米‧法倫今夜秀|吉米‧法倫今夜秀}}」與「[[艾倫·狄珍妮秀|艾倫·狄珍妮秀]]」。同月，她亦在「艾倫·狄珍妮秀」上演唱了兩首單曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-miley-cyrus-we-cant-stop-jimmy-fallon-roots-20131009-story.html|title=Watch Miley Cyrus sing 'We Can't Stop' with Jimmy Fallon, the Roots|last=Wood|first=Mikael|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2013-10-09|accessdate=2013-10-11}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.idolator.com/7488586/miley-cyrus-ellen-wrecking-ball|title=Miley Cyrus Takes Over 'Ellen': Watch Her Perform, Talk VMAs & Her Breakup|last=Williott|first=Carl|publisher=Idolator. Spin Medi