18|accessdate=2014-04-20}}</ref>。在該場表演獲得聲樂狀況不佳的批評後<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.heavy.com/entertainment/2013/11/miley-cyrus-x-factor-uk-2013-turban-wrecking-ball-odd/|title=Miley Cyrus Rocks Turban in Odd 'Wrecking Ball' X Factor Performance|last=Weigle|first=Lauren|publisher=Heavy|date=2013-11-17|accessdate=2014-04-20}}</ref>，希拉的醫生建議她在專輯的巡迴演唱會舉辦前進行「聲樂休息」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latinpost.com/articles/3893/20131119/miley-cyrus-bangerz-tour-update-doctors-order-stop-singing-ahead.htm|title=Miley Cyrus Bangerz Tour Update: Doctors Order Miley To Stop Singing Ahead of U.S. Tour|last=Jang|first=Esther|work=Latin Post|date=2013-11-19|accessdate=2013-11-20}}</ref>。11月24日，她在「[[2013年全美音乐奖|2013年全美音乐奖]]」上表演了〈愛情破壞球〉，並在投射一隻跟隨希拉口型的卡通貓大螢幕前演唱歌曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2013/11/24/amas-miley-cyrus-wrecking-ball|title=AMAs 2013: Miley Cyrus performs 'Wrecking Ball' with a giant cat|last=Franich|first=Darren|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2013-11-24|accessdate=2014-04-20}}</ref>。12月，她於[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]、[[圣保罗_(明尼苏达州)|圣保罗]]、[[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]、紐約市、[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]、[[坦帕|坦帕]]跟[[森赖斯_(佛罗里达州)|森赖斯]]舉行的多場「Jingle Ball演唱會」上表演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsday.com/business/press-releases/miley-cyrus-plans-2014-tour-superstartickets-com-announces-savings-on-miley-cyrus-tickets-1.6425460|title=Miley Cyrus Plans 2014 Tour – SuperStarTickets.com Announces Savings on Miley Cyrus Tickets|newspaper={{tsl|en|Newsday|Newsday|Newsday}}|publisher={{tsl|en|Cablevision|Cablevision|Cablevision}}|date=2013-11-12|accessdate=2013-11-16}}</ref>。而原本在[[波士顿|波士顿]]演唱的場次則因天氣問題導致航班取消而未能出席<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5847778/miley-cyrus-fans-seek-refund-for-no-show-at-boston-concert|title=Miley Cyrus Fans Seek Refund for No-Show at Boston Concert|last=Payne|first=Chris|work=Billboard|date=2013-12-20|accessdate=2013-12-21}}</ref>。

