ww.metrolyrics.com/news-story-see-what-songs-miley-cyrus-performed-on-mtvs-unplugged.html|title=See What Songs Miley Cyrus Performed On MTV's 'Unplugged'|last=Hutchison|first=Amanda|publisher=[[MetroLyrics|MetroLyrics]]|date=2014-01-30|accessdate=2014-04-20}}</ref>。該特輯的未審查版於2月6日在線上公開，並追加收錄翻唱自[[北極潑猴|北極潑猴]]的〈{{tsl|en|Why'd You Only Call Me When You're High?|Why'd You Only Call Me When You're High?|Why'd You Only Call Me When You're High?}}〉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/earshot/miley-cyrus-uncensored-mtv-unplugged-677724|title=Miley Cyrus' Uncensored 'MTV Unplugged' Performance Released (Video)|last=Lee|first=Ashley|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-02-06|accessdate=2014-02-06}}</ref>。5月27日，希拉於在[[蒙特卡洛|蒙特卡洛]]舉辦的「{{tsl|en|2014 World Music Awards|2014年世界音樂獎|2014年世界音樂獎}}」上演唱〈愛情破壞球〉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-style/news/miley-cyrus-world-music-awards-2014-ladylike-gowns-pictures-2014285|title=Miley Cyrus Looks Like a Lady in Dazzling Gowns at World Music Awards 2014: See Her Gorgeous Looks!|last=Tanenbaum|first=Shannon|work=Us Weekly|publisher=Wenner Media, LLC|date=2014-05-28|accessdate=2014-05-28}}</ref>。6月21日，希拉於在倫敦[[温布利球场|温布利球场]]舉辦的「{{tsl|en|Summertime Ball|Summertime Ball|Summertime Ball}}」演唱了〈炫耀曲線（派對大爆炸）〉、〈愛情 金錢 派對〉、〈愛情破壞球〉、〈青春大暴走〉跟〈{{tsl|en|Party in the U.S.A.|美國派對|美國派對}}〉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/miley-cyrus/news/summertime-ball-2014-setlist/|title=Miley Cyrus Brings Her Naughty Side – And Her Sister – To The Summertime Ball!|publisher={{tsl|en|Capital (radio network)|Capital Radio Network|Capital}}|date=2014-06-23|accessdate=2014-06-24}}</ref>。

== 巡迴演唱會 ==
